<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٣٠ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَسَأَلْتُ أَبَا إِسْحَاقَ الْفَزَارِيَّ عَنِ الْإِيمَانِ،<span class="c5"> فَقُلْتُ:</span> الْإِيمَانُ قَوْلٌ وَعَمَلٌ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَعَمْ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>